title: Trendessee: The Lolanteer Zeit 2/14: 'Love Is Blind', Snoop Dogg, A Day Without Immigrants, Sha'Carri Richardson, Academy Awards, Sarah Palin, Super Bowl Ads
itunes:title: Trendessee: The Lolanteer Zeit 2/14: 'Love Is Blind', Snoop Dogg, A Day Without Immigrants, Sha'Carri Richardson, Academy Awards, Sarah Palin, Super Bowl Ads
description:
In this edition of Trendessee: The Lolanteer Zeit, Jack and Miles discuss 'Love Is Blind' season 2, Snoop Dogg smoking weed before his Super Bowl performance?!?!, the 'Day Without Immigrants' protests, Sha'Carri Richardson calls out the doping double standard, this years panel of female hosts for the Oscars, Sarah Palin's defamation suit getting thrown out, and this years best Super Bowl ads.
